nhc_headline: ...HUMBERTO CONTINUES TO STRENGTHEN OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC... ...EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON FRIDAY...
summary: ...HUMBERTO CONTINUES TO STRENGTHEN OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC... ...EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON FRIDAY... As of 5:00 PM AST Thu Sep 25 the center of Humberto was located near 21.9, -57.0 with movement NW at 6 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1000 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
